                    <p class="date-updated">Mar 12, 2024</p>
                </div>
                <p>Art in Island is the Philippines' first and largest 3D interactive art museum located in Cubao, Quezon City. This unique museum features over 200 stunning 3D paintings where visitors become part of the artwork. From optical illusions to immersive scenes, every corner offers creative photo opportunities. The museum encourages touching and interacting with the art, making it a fun and engaging experience for all ages.</p>
            </section>

