                    <li>Over 200 interactive 3D paintings and optical illusions</li>
                    <li>Touch and pose with the artwork - cameras encouraged!</li>
                    <li>Various themed zones including safari, underwater, and fantasy</li>
                    <li>Professional lighting for perfect Instagram photos</li>
                    <li>Family-friendly attraction suitable for all ages</li>
                    <li>Air-conditioned galleries spanning multiple floors</li>
